  "keyFeatures": [
    "Dolt-powered version-controlled SQL database with cell-level merge",
    "Hash-based IDs prevent merge collisions in multi-agent workflows",
    "Dependency tracking with auto-ready task detection",
    "Persistent agent memory across sessions",
    "Semantic memory compaction to save context window",
    "Message threading with ephemeral lifecycle",
    "Graph links for knowledge graphs (relates_to, duplicates, supersedes)",
